"title": "8305: meekness",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8305",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>An attitude of humble, submissive and expectant trust in God, and a loving, patient and gentle attitude towards others.</p>\n<h2>Meekness required by God</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zeph2:3\">ZEP 2:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov16:19\">PRO 16:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet3:4\">1PE 3:4</a></p>\n<h2>God's promises to the meek</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps37:11\">PSA 37:11</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:5\">MAT 5:5</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet5:5\">1PE 5:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps25:9\">PSA 25:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps69:32\">PSA 69:32</a> <em>In Scripture, “the poor” frequently represent the humble, godly poor</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps147:6\">PSA 147:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa29:19\">ISA 29:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa66:2\">ISA 66:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zeph3:11-Zeph3:12\">ZEP 3:11–3:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas4:6\">JAS 4:6</a></p>\n<h2>God acts to save the meek</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps34:5-Ps34:6\">PSA 34:5–34:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam22:28\">2SA 22:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps10:12\">PSA 10:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps10:17\">PSA 10:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps18:27\">PSA 18:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps45:4\">PSA 45:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps76:9\">PSA 76:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps149:4\">PSA 149:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov3:34\">PRO 3:34</a></p>\n<h2>Meekness is a correct attitude in prayer</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps40:17\">PSA 40:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps70:5\">PSA 70:5</a></p>\n<h2>Godly wisdom produces meekness</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas3:13\">JAS 3:13</a></strong></p>\n<h2>Examples of meekness</h2>\n<h3>Moses</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num12:3\">NUM 12:3</a></strong></p>\n<h3>David</h3>\n<p><em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam16:11-2Sam16:12\">2SA 16:11–16:12</a></p>\n<h3>Ahab</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs21:27\">1KI 21:27</a></p>\n<h3>Job</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job1:21\">JOB 1:21</a></p>\n<h3>Jeremiah</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer11:19\">JER 11:19</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer26:14\">JER 26:14</a></p>\n<h3>Mary, the mother of Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:38\">LUK 1:38</a></p>\n<h3>Stephen</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts7:60\">ACT 7:60</a></p>\n<h3>Paul</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim4:16\">2TI 4:16</a></p>\n<h2>Meekness in the life of Jesus Christ</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt11:29\">MAT 11:29</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor10:1\">2CO 10:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa53:7\">ISA 53:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt21:5\">MAT 21:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark14:61\">MRK 14:61</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke23:34\">LUK 23:34</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:23\">1PE 2:23</a></p>\n<h2>Meekness is expected in the life of the Christian</h2>\n<h3>A necessary characteristic</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:2\">EPH 4:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal5:23\">GAL 5:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil2:3\">PHP 2:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil4:5\">PHP 4:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:12\">COL 3:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus3:2\">TIT 3:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet3:8\">1PE 3:8</a></p>\n<h3>Towards enemies</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:39-Matt5:41\">MAT 5:39–5:41</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:17-Rom12:20\">ROM 12:17–12:20</a></p>\n<h3>In leadership</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim6:11\">1TI 6:11</a></p>\n<h3>In witness</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet3:15\">1PE 3:15</a></p>\n<h3>In discipline</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal6:1\">GAL 6:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor4:21\">1CO 4:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim2:25\">2TI 2:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb5:2\">HEB 5:2</a></p>\n<h3>In the family</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:22\">EPH 5:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:24\">EPH 5:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph6:1\">EPH 6:1</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:18-Col3:20\">COL 3:18–3:20</a></p>\n<h3>In society</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom13:1-Rom13:2\">ROM 13:1–13:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom13:5\">ROM 13:5</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim2:2\">1TI 2:2</a></p>",
